529.
1191Hetu ajjhattārammaṇo dhammo hetussa ajjhattārammaṇassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
530.
1192Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe…  upanissaye āsevane nava, kamme tīṇi, vipāke nava, āhāre tīṇi, indriye nava, jhāne tīṇi, magge nava…pe…  avigate nava. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
